title: A true relation of His Majesties private departure from Hampton-Court, the eleventh of November, betweene foure and five of the clock in the after-noone. As it was delivered to the House of Commons this morning, Novemb. 12. by Sir Iohn Cook, and Master Crew, two of the commissioners. With the Houses resolution thereupon.
author: Charles I, King of England, 1600-1649.
